snippet.textDisplay:
Thanks for watching my descent into madness and pain, everyone!
Epilogue:
It took me four days to walk normally again, but that day I played soccer and felt very strong. Also, I knew this was a bad idea and actually did it to show what NOT to do. Don’t do 10k squats lol. But hopefully this entertained and inspired you on your own fitness journey 🍑🍑🍑
